<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>

    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <meta name="author" content="">

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", media: "all",
    "data-turbolinks-track" => 'reload' %>
        <%= javascript_include_tag "application", "data-turbolinks-track" => 'reload' %>
            <%= csrf_meta_tags %>

                <title>About</title>

                <!-- Bootstrap core CSS-->                
                <link href="css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
                <link href="css/round-about.css" rel="stylesheet">
                
                <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
                <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>              
                <link href="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet">                
</head>

<body>
    <%= render "layouts/frmheader-about" %>

        <div class="top-background-about">
            <div class="photos cleafix" style="transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);">
                <div class="photo">
                    <%= image_tag  "top-about/1.png" %>
                </div>

                <div class="photo">
                    <%= image_tag  "top-about/2.png" %>
                </div>
                <div class="photo">
                    <%= image_tag  "top-about/3.png" %>
                </div>
                <div class="photo">
                    <%= image_tag  "top-about/4.png" %>
                </div>
                <div class="photo">
                    <%= image_tag  "top-about/5.png" %>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="center">
                <div class="intro">
                    <h1 class="on-image">The place for photographers to grow</h1>
                    <p class="on-image">500px helps over 12 million photographers expand their creative networks of friends, colleagues and mentors,
                        learn new technical and aesthetic skills, and make money doing what they love.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <ul class="dots five">
                <li>
                    <a>
                        <span>1</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a>
                        <span>2</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a>
                        <span>3</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a>
                        <span>4</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a>
                        <span>5</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- About Content -->
        <div class="container">
            <!-- Introduction Row -->
            <section class="About-Prev-Tab">
                <h1 class="my-4"> Share Your Passion to the World
                </h1>
                <p>
                    From mobile photographers to professionals, ViewIt has the products and features to take your photography to the next level.

                </p>
            </section>

            <!-- Team Members Row -->
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <h2 class="my-4">Our Team</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 text-center mb-4">
                    <%= image_tag  "taibeo.png", size: "200x200", :class => "rounded-circle img-fluid d-block mx-auto" %>
                        <h3>Tài Béo
                            <small></small>
                        </h3>
                        <p>Cold Blood with True Love</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 text-center mb-4">
                    <%= image_tag  "bathanh.png", size: "200x200", :class => "rounded-circle img-fluid d-block mx-auto" %>
                        <h3>Bá Thành
                            <small></small>
                        </h3>
                        <p>What does this team member to? Keep it short! This is also a great spot for social links!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 text-center mb-4">
                    <%= image_tag  "phatle.png", size: "200x200", :class => "rounded-circle img-fluid d-block mx-auto" %>
                        <h3>Phát Lê
                            <small></small>
                        </h3>
                        <p>What does this team member to? Keep it short! This is also a great spot for social links!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- /.container -->
</body>

</html>